WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 20=

01:43.990 --> 01:46.820
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

02:23.140 --> 02:23.980
Your Grace,

02:25.740 --> 02:26.580
I've figured it out.

02:26.860 --> 02:27.990
Indeed, some lords

02:28.700 --> 02:30.390
falsified the roster

02:30.790 --> 02:32.350
to fulfill the Ascension Decree.

02:33.070 --> 02:34.230
I've punished them by the law.

02:34.990 --> 02:36.740
But there's still no clue
to the formation

02:37.140 --> 02:38.180
in the Void Valley.

02:38.860 --> 02:40.950
He and I had all temples investigated.

02:40.950 --> 02:42.510
No other spirits have been missing.

02:42.670 --> 02:43.670
Everything is as usual.

02:44.990 --> 02:46.230
The warrior in the tournament,

02:47.180 --> 02:48.740
the puppet spirit that lured me,

02:49.420 --> 02:51.180
and the formation that trapped Yan and me...

02:52.070 --> 02:52.990
The power of the three

02:52.990 --> 02:54.700
all comes from Chiling Secret Technique.

02:55.670 --> 02:57.270
I guess someone set a trap

02:57.620 --> 02:58.990
to drain my power at first.

02:58.990 --> 02:59.860
Then when I was weak,

02:59.860 --> 03:01.070
he could kill me.

03:03.460 --> 03:04.670
Not too stupid.

03:05.300 --> 03:06.460
No wonder those spirits

03:06.860 --> 03:09.140
can cast spells
with mediocre spirit power.

03:09.510 --> 03:11.070
So someone manipulated them.

03:11.620 --> 03:12.480
To control this,

03:12.480 --> 03:14.620
one must have abundant power.

03:14.830 --> 03:16.860
This technique is mysterious too.

03:17.230 --> 03:18.180
In the Void,

03:18.460 --> 03:19.860
very few spirits are powerful enough

03:19.860 --> 03:20.950
to learn this technique.

03:21.510 --> 03:22.900
The one who had immense power

03:23.950 --> 03:25.300
and assassinated the Sovereign

03:25.300 --> 03:26.460
so blatantly.

03:27.070 --> 03:28.900
It could

03:28.900 --> 03:29.860
only be Bai Sanxing.

03:31.830 --> 03:32.990
But Her Grace confirmed

03:33.460 --> 03:34.390
that Bai Sanxing

03:34.990 --> 03:36.110
was dead.

03:40.900 --> 03:42.300
White Terror was formidable

03:42.300 --> 03:43.420
and vengeful.

03:45.180 --> 03:46.230
If he isn't dead

03:47.300 --> 03:48.300
and has power again,

03:49.390 --> 03:51.020
he'll make a comeback.

03:52.350 --> 03:53.390
Unfortunately,

03:55.580 --> 03:57.140
the three of us jointly sent him

03:57.140 --> 03:58.830
into the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

03:59.390 --> 04:00.270
It was also me

04:00.790 --> 04:02.700
who destroyed his soul candle in person.

04:03.620 --> 04:04.950
A spirit without his soul candle

04:04.950 --> 04:06.140
will definitely be lost

04:06.140 --> 04:07.460
in the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

04:07.460 --> 04:09.420
He'll be annihilated within a century.

04:10.070 --> 04:10.950
Bai Sanxing

04:11.460 --> 04:12.420
must be dead.

04:14.350 --> 04:15.510
In that case,

04:15.950 --> 04:17.860
another powerful spirit here

04:18.380 --> 04:20.060
is eyeing Her Grace covetously.

04:31.420 --> 04:33.180
I need to recuperate for some time.

04:34.180 --> 04:35.060
During this period,

04:35.470 --> 04:36.820
I'll count on the two of you

04:37.180 --> 04:38.590
to manage all the affairs.

04:40.300 --> 04:41.140
Yes.

04:53.380 --> 04:54.590
Young man, don't be stubborn.

04:55.590 --> 04:57.230
Simu has had heavy affairs lately

04:57.470 --> 04:59.230
and can't have both in many cases.

04:59.990 --> 05:01.300
Go back and get some rest.

05:03.590 --> 05:04.430
Are you here

05:05.350 --> 05:06.670
with leads on the assassination?

05:06.910 --> 05:08.180
When you're shut out,

05:08.180 --> 05:09.620
why do you still worry about this?

05:10.860 --> 05:12.180
I'm just standing out here.

05:12.740 --> 05:14.030
I'm not expelled from the Void.

05:20.820 --> 05:22.500
Do you remember the last two spirits

05:22.500 --> 05:23.500
in the Void Tournament?

05:24.910 --> 05:26.620
They fell under a secret spell.

05:27.030 --> 05:28.620
This spell is probably related

05:28.620 --> 05:30.550
to guilty spirits
in the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

05:31.030 --> 05:31.910
Nine-Square Maze Prison?

05:32.380 --> 05:34.030
That's the place spirits fear most.

05:34.360 --> 05:35.220
A prison

05:35.230 --> 05:36.620
for those guilty of grave offenses.

05:37.470 --> 05:39.790
It originated from inner darkness.

05:40.260 --> 05:41.940
Any spirit who is jailed there

05:41.940 --> 05:43.300
will be deprived of his soul candle

05:43.590 --> 05:44.820
and get lost in the sins

05:44.820 --> 05:46.030
fabricated by the Prison.

05:46.620 --> 05:48.380
He'll be tortured by obsessions

05:48.380 --> 05:49.990
of doing everything he hates most

05:49.990 --> 05:51.470
until he's annihilated.

05:52.150 --> 05:53.060
This is the last place

05:53.060 --> 05:54.470
where spirits want to go.

05:54.710 --> 05:56.710
Only Simu dares to go there at times.

05:57.790 --> 05:58.820
I just don't know

05:58.820 --> 05:59.940
why she goes there.

06:03.740 --> 06:04.600
Maybe she cares

06:04.620 --> 06:05.740
about something inside it.

06:08.910 --> 06:10.300
Don't overthink it.

06:10.300 --> 06:11.500
Go back and get some sleep.

06:11.790 --> 06:13.260
Don't waste the efforts Simu made

06:13.260 --> 06:15.110
to cure your cold poison.

06:41.380 --> 06:42.500
I shouldn't have acted alone

06:42.910 --> 06:44.060
to spoil your plan.

06:48.940 --> 06:49.860
I'm sorry.

06:49.860 --> 06:50.700
I was wrong.

06:51.350 --> 06:52.230
I won't do it again.

06:52.620 --> 06:53.460
I was wrong.

06:54.300 --> 06:55.300
I'll never do it again.

06:57.790 --> 06:58.630
I was wrong.

07:56.230 --> 07:57.070
Simu.

07:58.910 --> 07:59.750
Simu.

08:02.110 --> 08:03.230
You finally let me in.

08:05.180 --> 08:06.030
After the Tournament,

08:06.820 --> 08:08.030
I found two weird spirits.

08:08.750 --> 08:09.590
With a strange smell,

08:09.590 --> 08:10.620
they were like the two

08:11.030 --> 08:12.060
that drained your power.

08:12.940 --> 08:14.550
I followed them to Xuling Temple.

08:15.060 --> 08:15.900
They disappeared.

08:16.470 --> 08:17.310
I think Xuling Temple

08:17.500 --> 08:18.340
is behind this.

08:20.230 --> 08:21.070
Are you done?

08:25.710 --> 08:27.110
Then take the decoction.

08:27.790 --> 08:28.910
After this treatment,

08:29.110 --> 08:30.620
your cold poison will be cured.

08:34.190 --> 08:35.260
Your power is diminished

08:35.260 --> 08:36.100
and hasn't come back.

08:36.660 --> 08:37.830
You could cure my cold poison,

08:38.430 --> 08:39.350
but there's no rush.

08:45.340 --> 08:46.180
Don't you

08:46.190 --> 08:47.040
have anything to say?

08:55.780 --> 08:56.830
If you don't,

08:57.710 --> 08:58.550
I'll say something.

08:59.990 --> 09:00.830
Simu.

09:02.830 --> 09:04.070
Can you let me help you too?

09:05.260 --> 09:06.660
Like how you helped me in my world.

09:07.740 --> 09:09.020
Let me do something for you.

09:20.310 --> 09:21.710
How can you help me?

09:23.380 --> 09:25.190
Mortals who have five senses like you

09:25.190 --> 09:26.140
are everywhere.

09:27.190 --> 09:28.710
What makes you special?

09:29.900 --> 09:30.950
Because of our spell,

09:33.310 --> 09:34.740
you think you're unique?

09:37.500 --> 09:38.860
Maybe you're invincible in battles

09:38.860 --> 09:39.830
of the Mortal World.

09:41.430 --> 09:42.500
But right here,

09:43.950 --> 09:46.230
you're a small and insignificant mortal.

09:58.310 --> 09:59.190
After you cure me,

10:00.660 --> 10:01.500
what will you do?

10:08.380 --> 10:09.220
Drink it.

10:32.020 --> 10:33.710
So your power has come back.

10:35.140 --> 10:36.660
From the Mortal World to the Void,

10:37.490 --> 10:38.350
no one can

10:38.350 --> 10:39.620
actually harm me.

10:41.350 --> 10:42.620
You don't know enough about me.

10:44.540 --> 10:46.020
I still have time to get to know you.

10:46.740 --> 10:47.580
No, you don't.

10:48.230 --> 10:49.190
You don't belong here.

10:55.470 --> 10:56.470
In that case,

10:57.430 --> 10:58.270
why did you allow me

10:58.710 --> 11:00.020
to come here?

11:00.540 --> 11:01.950
Why did you indulge my every move?

11:03.140 --> 11:03.990
You just...

11:03.990 --> 11:05.310
Since you're so curious,

11:06.780 --> 11:07.860
I'm telling you now.

11:48.380 --> 11:49.950
I just had a fleeting fancy.

11:51.140 --> 11:52.470
Now I'm no longer interested.

11:54.740 --> 11:55.660
Since that kiss

11:55.660 --> 11:57.230
gets you to think so much,

11:58.860 --> 11:59.950
this kiss

11:59.950 --> 12:00.900
will put an end.

12:05.020 --> 12:05.990
Tomorrow, Jiang Ai

12:05.990 --> 12:06.830
will send you back.

12:07.710 --> 12:08.740
Everything between us...

12:10.070 --> 12:11.190
Keep it if you want.

12:12.110 --> 12:13.350
Otherwise, I will take it away.

12:16.430 --> 12:17.710
Drop such unrealistic ideas

12:17.710 --> 12:18.550
like helping me.

12:24.900 --> 12:25.740
Foxy,

12:27.660 --> 12:28.950
take the experiences

12:30.590 --> 12:31.440
over this period

12:31.450 --> 12:32.620
as a twist of fate.

14:10.310 --> 14:11.620
Say my name.

14:12.590 --> 14:14.950
Jiang... Jiang Ai.

14:30.020 --> 14:31.780
What a good mood you're in.

14:34.430 --> 14:36.660
You're in a great mood too.

14:37.230 --> 14:39.430
You visit me even during the curfew.

14:39.990 --> 14:41.110
To what do I owe this honor?

14:41.780 --> 14:42.900
You're truly devoted

14:42.900 --> 14:44.660
to Bai Sanxing.

14:45.470 --> 14:46.740
It's been over 300 years

14:46.740 --> 14:47.860
and you can't forget him.

14:48.710 --> 14:49.780
It must have been hard

14:50.110 --> 14:51.190
to bear all this time

14:51.620 --> 14:53.110
before you assassinated Her Grace

14:53.110 --> 14:54.260
to avenge him.

14:57.230 --> 14:58.500
You assist Her Grace

14:58.500 --> 14:59.830
in implementing the decrees.

15:00.070 --> 15:02.380
How could you speak without evidence?

15:02.900 --> 15:04.590
Why would I assassinate Her Grace

15:04.590 --> 15:06.190
to avenge Bai Sanxing?

15:08.230 --> 15:09.310
Bai Sanxing and you

15:09.310 --> 15:10.660
had your differences,

15:12.020 --> 15:13.260
but I believe

15:13.260 --> 15:14.740
you quite enjoyed it.

15:24.260 --> 15:26.070
You and Bai Sanxing

15:26.180 --> 15:27.020
also shared

15:27.020 --> 15:28.780
an unbreakable bond from the past.

15:29.830 --> 15:31.540
After all, you were

15:31.540 --> 15:33.350
his most capable vice lord.

15:34.020 --> 15:35.190
In that case,

15:35.710 --> 15:37.540
you and I are not so different.

15:38.140 --> 15:39.660
Every thirty years,

15:40.430 --> 15:41.830
you wander

15:41.830 --> 15:42.860
around the Prison.

15:43.380 --> 15:45.380
No one but Bai Sanxing

15:45.380 --> 15:46.740
is so hard for you to let go of.

15:48.140 --> 15:49.310
In that case,

15:49.990 --> 15:51.660
don't you want to avenge him?

15:52.350 --> 15:54.500
You used to be utterly loyal

15:54.500 --> 15:55.710
to Bai Sanxing.

15:56.110 --> 15:58.260
In the end, you still betrayed him

15:58.260 --> 15:59.430
for the sake of power.

16:00.350 --> 16:01.660
I guess you've never been loyal

16:01.660 --> 16:03.350
to Bai Sanxing

16:03.500 --> 16:04.860
or He Simu.

16:05.260 --> 16:06.430
You're loyal

16:06.430 --> 16:07.430
only to yourself.

16:08.500 --> 16:09.900
Maybe you've betrayed

16:09.900 --> 16:11.190
your new master

16:11.470 --> 16:13.350
just to get more power.

16:18.020 --> 16:19.470
You schemed

16:20.070 --> 16:21.380
to get close to that mortal

16:21.950 --> 16:23.380
just to use him

16:23.540 --> 16:24.430
as bait

16:24.710 --> 16:25.900
to enter the Prison

16:25.900 --> 16:27.500
for the man you want to see.

16:29.230 --> 16:31.140
This is what we call real betrayal.

17:35.540 --> 17:36.470
You've been amazing.

17:37.820 --> 17:38.820
You were,

17:40.260 --> 17:41.100
and you still are.

17:44.190 --> 17:45.430
Are you not used to it

17:45.950 --> 17:47.100
when I'm not around?

17:53.780 --> 17:54.620
Farewell.

17:58.150 --> 17:59.060
Foxy.

18:34.580 --> 18:35.420
Your Ladyship.

18:37.150 --> 18:38.430
Did you come to ask me

18:38.430 --> 18:39.580
to send you away?

18:40.390 --> 18:41.230
Wait a minute.

18:41.430 --> 18:42.270
I'll arrange it now.

18:42.630 --> 18:43.630
You once promised

18:44.230 --> 18:45.580
you would take me anywhere.

18:47.230 --> 18:48.070
Does it still count?

19:10.430 --> 19:12.100
Last time when Simu and I came here,

19:12.430 --> 19:13.630
we didn't go this deep.

19:14.500 --> 19:15.340
Young man,

19:15.470 --> 19:17.020
it's not too late to regret now.

19:38.990 --> 19:39.830
Xusheng,

19:40.430 --> 19:41.270
wake up.

19:47.940 --> 19:51.580
(Xusheng, the Void)

19:59.190 --> 20:01.470
The mountain spirit is named Xusheng.
[*Means the void]

20:01.870 --> 20:03.820
That's why this is the Void Mountain.

20:05.190 --> 20:06.340
The entire mountain

20:06.340 --> 20:08.190
was transformed from his body.

20:08.630 --> 20:10.230
His eyes are the gate.

20:10.820 --> 20:11.990
The Nine-Square Maze Prison

20:11.990 --> 20:13.670
is inside his skull.

20:14.580 --> 20:15.540
Are you saying

20:16.580 --> 20:18.300
we're going into his skull?

20:25.060 --> 20:27.390
Identify yourselves.

20:28.300 --> 20:30.820
I'm Lord Jiang Ai of Xuling Temple.

20:33.190 --> 20:34.340
Jiang Ai?

20:34.710 --> 20:36.060
What a rare visitor.

20:37.150 --> 20:38.820
What crime did you commit?

20:39.500 --> 20:40.780
Why haven't I received

20:40.780 --> 20:42.950
Her Grace's decree?

20:43.540 --> 20:44.470
Xusheng,

20:44.780 --> 20:46.300
don't be ridiculous.

20:46.710 --> 20:48.430
I'm a good spirit,

20:48.430 --> 20:49.870
sensible and law-abiding.

20:49.870 --> 20:50.990
How could I go to prison?

20:51.430 --> 20:53.910
I just want to take a look in there

20:54.300 --> 20:55.780
with my friend.

21:04.060 --> 21:06.950
He has Her Grace's aura.

21:07.710 --> 21:09.470
Very strong.

21:10.580 --> 21:13.950
And he's a mortal.

21:14.540 --> 21:17.020
I can't let him in.

21:18.390 --> 21:19.500
You're right.

21:20.500 --> 21:21.390
However,

21:21.390 --> 21:23.190
Her Grace might acknowledge him.

21:27.470 --> 21:28.310
That's right.

21:28.820 --> 21:29.780
Simu and I

21:30.340 --> 21:31.500
have a lifelong commitment.

21:32.950 --> 21:34.230
The last mortal

21:34.230 --> 21:36.020
who had the Sovereign's aura

21:36.020 --> 21:38.020
was the wife of the former sovereign.

21:38.740 --> 21:41.100
Fine. In you come.

21:58.150 --> 21:59.390
Take good care of this.

21:59.540 --> 22:00.950
This is your soul candle.

22:05.670 --> 22:07.020
Only by holding this

22:07.150 --> 22:08.100
will you not get lost

22:08.100 --> 22:09.580
in the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

22:32.870 --> 22:33.710
Young man,

22:34.150 --> 22:35.430
are you sure you'll get in there?

22:41.500 --> 22:42.540
Did Simu ever say

22:43.500 --> 22:44.340
I couldn't get in?

22:53.100 --> 22:54.190
There's complete darkness

22:55.470 --> 22:56.820
inside this prison.

22:58.150 --> 22:59.340
When you hold the soul candle,

22:59.500 --> 23:00.430
all you can see

23:00.430 --> 23:01.870
is boundless darkness.

23:03.060 --> 23:04.580
Only when your candle dies out

23:05.100 --> 23:07.300
can you see the real prison.

23:10.020 --> 23:12.020
In the Nine-Square Maze Prison,

23:12.190 --> 23:14.430
evil spirits' desires are amplified.

23:15.190 --> 23:17.100
The most painful and repeated illusions

23:17.300 --> 23:18.990
have been created for them,

23:18.990 --> 23:20.020
luring them to chase.

23:20.430 --> 23:21.990
But they can't obtain anything.

23:25.870 --> 23:27.430
Hope is given and then crushed.

23:28.860 --> 23:29.710
It's like a donkey

23:29.710 --> 23:30.870
with an apple dangling above.

23:31.780 --> 23:32.630
It can see the apple

23:33.540 --> 23:34.540
but can never eat it.

23:35.430 --> 23:37.230
That's a fitting way to put it.

23:38.580 --> 23:40.540
Young man, I admire you.

23:42.300 --> 23:43.150
For Simu's sake,

23:43.160 --> 23:44.670
you even dare to come in here.

23:54.580 --> 23:56.950
But mortals are different from spirits.

23:58.190 --> 23:59.540
Before, you asked me

23:59.540 --> 24:00.670
about Simu's past.

24:01.430 --> 24:03.470
She's been living for 400 years.

24:03.470 --> 24:04.310
400 years.

24:04.500 --> 24:06.870
It includes more than 146,000

24:06.870 --> 24:07.820
days and nights.

24:08.470 --> 24:10.910
Like a book with 146,000 pages.

24:12.150 --> 24:13.150
Can you understand her?

24:17.950 --> 24:18.910
She said I needn't.

24:20.060 --> 24:21.020
Possibly because

24:22.740 --> 24:23.740
she thinks I can't do it.

24:28.470 --> 24:30.390
This prison is terrifying,

24:30.910 --> 24:31.820
but when we follow

24:31.820 --> 24:33.190
the Eight Trigrams,

24:33.470 --> 24:34.950
we'll find the Life Gate and leave.

24:36.470 --> 24:37.310
Your Ladyship,

24:38.100 --> 24:38.940
I heard something.

25:05.630 --> 25:06.470
Bai Sanxing,

25:06.670 --> 25:07.740
you aren't annihilated yet?

25:19.710 --> 25:20.580
Young man, move aside.

25:20.710 --> 25:21.630
You can't take him.

25:38.580 --> 25:40.020
Watch out, young man!

25:53.580 --> 25:54.420
Your Ladyship,

25:55.500 --> 25:56.500
shall we bet again?

25:56.720 --> 25:57.590
If I can get out

25:57.590 --> 25:58.630
of this prison alive,

25:59.340 --> 26:00.190
tell me everything

26:00.190 --> 26:01.030
about Simu's past.

26:01.540 --> 26:02.380
Deal?

26:05.870 --> 26:06.780
Don't be ridiculous.

26:06.990 --> 26:08.150
Without the soul candle,

26:08.150 --> 26:09.580
how can you get out of the illusion?

26:10.150 --> 26:10.990
Duan Xu,

26:10.990 --> 26:11.830
I accept the bet!

26:12.060 --> 26:13.540
Make sure you come out alive!

26:18.540 --> 26:19.780
As you expected, Your Grace,

26:19.910 --> 26:20.750
something's wrong.

26:21.340 --> 26:22.540
All the spirits

26:22.540 --> 26:23.390
match the records.

26:23.910 --> 26:24.750
But some of them only

26:25.100 --> 26:26.580
remember going to the Ascension Pool,

26:27.100 --> 26:28.020
but nothing after that.

26:28.870 --> 26:30.100
I suspect these spirits

26:30.710 --> 26:31.550
were manipulated.

26:32.870 --> 26:34.020
This is one of them.

26:35.260 --> 26:36.230
I interrogated him.

26:36.630 --> 26:37.470
Sadly,

26:38.580 --> 26:39.580
I got nothing out of him.

27:07.970 --> 27:09.660
Simu.

27:09.820 --> 27:10.710
Your Grace,

27:10.710 --> 27:12.100
Bai Sanxing isn't annihilated yet.

27:12.100 --> 27:13.300
He's still in the Prison.

27:15.150 --> 27:16.430
You went there?

27:17.910 --> 27:18.990
And you saw him.

27:20.260 --> 27:22.300
That young man of yours...

27:22.870 --> 27:24.340
Bai Sanxing broke his soul candle,

27:24.580 --> 27:25.990
and he's lost there.

27:27.540 --> 27:28.380
What happened?

27:31.100 --> 27:32.230
I don't think

27:33.340 --> 27:34.820
he can make it back.

27:46.150 --> 27:47.430
Your Grace, it's all my fault.

27:47.430 --> 27:48.390
I failed to protect him.

27:49.250 --> 27:50.100
Going in to find him?

27:50.100 --> 27:50.940
Simu,

27:51.190 --> 27:52.150
he's lost his candle.

27:52.370 --> 27:53.230
Even if you go in,

27:53.230 --> 27:54.100
you won't find him.

27:54.100 --> 27:54.940
Even if you find him,

27:54.940 --> 27:55.990
you can't get him out.

27:56.340 --> 27:57.740
Besides, Bai Sanxing is in there.

27:57.990 --> 27:58.910
If he does anything,

27:58.910 --> 27:59.820
you'll be in danger.

28:00.340 --> 28:01.430
You think I'll be scared?

28:01.740 --> 28:02.990
I don't want you to risk it.

28:03.500 --> 28:04.500
Even a powerful spirit

28:04.500 --> 28:06.060
will be annihilated if he's lost.

28:06.060 --> 28:07.390
A mortal will die in there.

28:07.990 --> 28:09.190
And this prison

28:09.190 --> 28:10.780
is filled with delusional evil spirits.

28:11.140 --> 28:11.990
A living man in there

28:11.990 --> 28:13.190
will be torn apart.

28:13.540 --> 28:14.950
He's lost in the illusion.

28:14.960 --> 28:15.840
Without a soul candle,

28:15.840 --> 28:17.150
he can't get out of this prison.

28:18.150 --> 28:19.100
He doesn't die easily.

28:19.630 --> 28:20.740
His fate is linked to mine.

28:21.230 --> 28:22.150
If I can find him

28:22.580 --> 28:23.430
and relight his candle

28:23.430 --> 28:24.670
with mine,

28:25.060 --> 28:26.340
he may regain consciousness.

28:26.670 --> 28:27.510
Simu!

28:28.990 --> 28:30.260
Using your soul candle?

28:30.630 --> 28:31.820
If he doesn't wake up,

28:31.820 --> 28:32.990
but extinguishes your candle,

28:32.990 --> 28:33.830
what will happen?

28:33.840 --> 28:34.950
You'll be lost in there

28:34.950 --> 28:36.020
and suffer forever.

28:36.910 --> 28:38.630
Do you want to end up like Bai Sanxing?

28:39.390 --> 28:40.540
I'm not letting you go!

28:42.150 --> 28:43.190
He's a mortal.

28:43.500 --> 28:44.500
He'll die.

28:47.820 --> 28:48.820
The longer he stays,

28:48.820 --> 28:50.190
the more dangerous it will be.

28:51.390 --> 28:52.230
How can you

28:52.230 --> 28:53.100
take such a risk

28:53.100 --> 28:54.020
for a mere mortal?

28:54.020 --> 28:55.470
He isn't a mere mortal.

28:55.740 --> 28:56.950
He's my spell bearer.

28:56.950 --> 28:58.100
He belongs to me.

28:59.990 --> 29:00.950
When I want him to live,

29:01.470 --> 29:02.540
then he shall not die.

29:06.470 --> 29:07.340
Xusheng,

29:07.340 --> 29:08.230
give me a soul candle.

29:23.820 --> 29:24.990
Spell bearer?

29:25.910 --> 29:27.260
The one who can lend her

29:27.260 --> 29:28.340
his five senses?

29:30.540 --> 29:32.190
Simu. Simu!

29:32.190 --> 29:33.340
You know very well.

29:34.430 --> 29:35.270
You can't stop her.

31:01.580 --> 31:03.060
(This is what this prison looks like)

31:04.300 --> 31:05.580
(after my soul candle dies out.)

31:18.540 --> 31:19.380
Kill.

31:20.710 --> 31:21.580
He Simu.

31:22.340 --> 31:23.260
I'll kill you!

31:24.060 --> 31:24.900
He Simu,

31:25.470 --> 31:26.310
I'll kill you.

31:26.990 --> 31:28.060
He Simu.

31:30.230 --> 31:31.340
Kill.

31:32.150 --> 31:33.340
- You know Simu?
- Kill her.

31:34.740 --> 31:35.740
I deserve to be

31:36.470 --> 31:37.740
the Sovereign!

31:40.870 --> 31:41.710
Kill.

31:42.430 --> 31:43.270
Kill.

31:43.280 --> 31:44.210
Who did you teach

31:44.500 --> 31:45.780
the technique for killing Simu

31:46.340 --> 31:47.180
in the tournament?

31:51.340 --> 31:52.180
Mortal?

31:54.150 --> 31:55.100
You're a mortal.

32:13.230 --> 32:14.070
Answer me.

32:33.580 --> 32:34.420
Get out.

32:36.060 --> 32:36.900
I want to get out.

34:34.750 --> 34:35.590
Simu.

35:22.220 --> 35:23.060
Father.

35:23.470 --> 35:24.790
Father, help me!

35:25.430 --> 35:26.270
Help me!

35:26.480 --> 35:27.350
Father.

35:27.350 --> 35:28.190
I won't help you.

35:29.140 --> 35:30.060
Climb out on your own.

35:30.580 --> 35:31.540
Help me!

35:31.540 --> 35:32.500
Give me your hand!

35:33.470 --> 35:34.660
My son is in Daizhou,

35:35.540 --> 35:36.950
staying with his grandmother.

35:37.620 --> 35:38.500
You got the wrong boy.

35:39.350 --> 35:41.060
Father, give me your hand!

36:17.180 --> 36:18.020
Simu,

36:18.830 --> 36:19.670
there you are.

36:24.990 --> 36:25.830
Mortal,

36:27.180 --> 36:29.540
you just don't give up on me, do you?

36:29.990 --> 36:30.830
Yeah.

36:31.060 --> 36:32.140
So I came to the Void

36:33.220 --> 36:34.500
and even entered this prison.

36:35.020 --> 36:36.310
Have you enjoyed yourself?

36:37.950 --> 36:38.790
If you have,

36:39.350 --> 36:40.190
then leave.

36:41.830 --> 36:42.910
Leave the Void.

36:43.470 --> 36:44.310
Simu,

36:45.140 --> 36:45.990
don't you want senses?

36:47.020 --> 36:48.220
I'll always lend you my senses.

36:54.060 --> 36:55.060
Having your senses

36:55.060 --> 36:56.500
is just a game.

37:21.350 --> 37:22.270
I'm fed up now.

37:24.140 --> 37:24.980
You should go.

37:39.580 --> 37:40.420
Duan Xu.

37:46.700 --> 37:47.620
Go find Duan Xu.

38:01.020 --> 38:01.990
Duan Xu.

38:07.950 --> 38:09.270
You're inside an illusion

38:09.830 --> 38:10.830
and everything is fake.

38:11.310 --> 38:12.150
I'm taking you out.

38:31.470 --> 38:32.310
Duan Xu,

38:33.500 --> 38:34.350
I'm He Simu.

38:38.580 --> 38:39.420
Duan Xu,

38:39.830 --> 38:40.700
I'm He Simu.

38:41.350 --> 38:42.350
I'm He Simu.

38:46.500 --> 38:47.340
Foxy,

38:48.750 --> 38:49.590
wake up.

38:50.220 --> 38:51.060
Foxy,

38:51.580 --> 38:52.500
wake up now.

39:06.430 --> 39:07.270
Foxy,

39:09.060 --> 39:10.270
you're too lost in illusion.

39:34.060 --> 39:34.900
(The sense of touch.)

39:35.660 --> 39:36.830
(I have this sense again.)

39:48.540 --> 39:49.470
(Even the sense of smell.)

39:50.910 --> 39:51.870
(I can smell again.)

40:14.620 --> 40:15.460
Simu.

40:20.580 --> 40:21.420
You're awake.

40:22.060 --> 40:22.900
Come have breakfast.

40:30.100 --> 40:30.940
What's wrong?

40:31.990 --> 40:32.830
Don't space out.

40:33.750 --> 40:34.590
Come have breakfast.

40:44.920 --> 40:50.250
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:50.580 --> 40:54.830
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:56.190 --> 41:01.560
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:01.860 --> 41:06.460
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:07.550 --> 41:09.390
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:21.600 --> 41:27.040
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

41:27.220 --> 41:31.550
♪Light encountered shadow♪

41:32.920 --> 41:38.310
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:38.540 --> 41:42.480
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:44.250 --> 41:46.140
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:48.800 --> 41:51.960
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

41:51.960 --> 41:54.490
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

41:54.490 --> 42:00.010
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

42:00.010 --> 42:03.250
♪Following fate's guidance♪

42:03.250 --> 42:08.110
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

42:08.450 --> 42:11.470
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

42:11.470 --> 42:14.290
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

42:14.550 --> 42:17.080
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

42:17.080 --> 42:22.500
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

42:22.670 --> 42:25.740
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

42:25.900 --> 42:30.800
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

42:31.010 --> 42:34.480
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
